Usage: reportVtInstCount [-help] [-area] [-leakage] [-outFile <fileName> [-detailed ] ]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-area                   # Print area distribution across libs in each VT
                        # partition (bool, optional)
-detailed               # Print complete detail in the file (bool, optional)
-leakage                # Print leakage distribution across libs in each VT
                        # partition (bool, optional)
-outFile <fileName>     # Print the output in the file in the format required
                        # for user defined VT partitioning (string, optional)